WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:12.000
Design intent becomes a reviewable, schema-backed proposal.

00:12.000 --> 00:24.000
Findings stay ordered, specific, and actionable.

00:24.000 --> 00:36.000
Rejection requires a rationale before it can be saved.

00:36.000 --> 00:48.000
Edited decisions retain a field-level diff.

00:48.000 --> 01:00.000
Only reviewed mappings can produce code or an Agent Brief.
